    Class Description
    DynamicProperties  
    DynamicProperties.Exceptions  
    GridGraphComputer
    GridGraph implementation of GraphComputer to support OLAP computing and parallel processing
    GridGraphComputer.Exceptions
    Common exceptions to use with a GridGraphComputer.
    GridGraphFilter
    GridGraph computing filter to prune the source graph data being loaded into the OLAP system.
    GridMapEmitter<K,V>
    GridGraph implementation of MapReduce.MapEmitter to emit key/value pairs from the map() stage of a MapReduce job.
    GridMemory
    GridGraph implementation of Memory, acting as a global data structure where by vertices can communicate information with one another.
    GridReduceEmitter<K,V>
    GridGraph implementation of MapReduce.ReduceEmitter to emit key/value pairs from the combine() and reduce() stages of a MapReduce job.
    GridVertexMessages<T>
    A GridVertexMessages represents graph computing (sub-)graph level global container of all messages sent between vertices.

    GridWorkerMemory
    GridGraph implementation of Memory for single worker.
